  "texts": [
    "CNNs have limitations in capturing long-range dependencies.",
    "However, the Transformer model, which first gained popularity in natural language processing, has been introduced to computer vision.",
    "Its advantage in capturing long-range dependencies has sparked a research trend in Vision Transformers.",
    "Aformer [45] adopts a Swin Transformer as the encoder with a pyramid structure to extract features at different stages and utilizes a multi-scale channel attention module to extract multi-scale feature information.",
    "DuAT [62] is a dual-aggregation Transformer network for polyp segmentation, which aggregates global and local spatial features and locates multi-scale objects."
  ],
  "correct_citations": [
    "Aformer [45] adopts a Swin Transformer as the encoder with a pyramid structure to extract features at different stages and utilizes a multi-scale channel attention module to extract multi-scale feature information.",
